{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This is a fast-paced first-person shooter game where players can utilize fully destructible environments, such as breaking walls, furniture, and obstacles, to devise tactical strategies and develop their own combat style to defeat pixel monsters invading from the virtual game world into reality. Additionally, we've incorporated 3D bullet-hell shooting and roguelite level mechanisms to provide players with a thrilling, stress-relieving, and cathartic combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Key Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Destruction- All objects in the scene can be destroyed, including the floor, and even the entire level can be completely eliminated.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explosions- Unique 3D pixel explosion effects provide exhilarating combat and the satisfaction of total destruction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Custom &quot;Classes&quot;- Freely combine guns, skills, and items to find the setup that suits your style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monster Destruction- Monsters can be destroyed just like the environment.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dynamic Levels- Environmental destruction mechanics offer more tactical experiences and varied gameplay.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/3.gif?t=1738494697\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/100_6.gif?t=1738494697\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/extras/100_19.gif?t=1738494697\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3143510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738494697","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/stor